FBIS4-58793 "drnes089dd_94015" FBIS-NES-94-089 Daily Report 8 May 1994 Palestinian Affairs 'Arafat Issues Decree on Status of Civil Servants 'Arafat Issues Decree on Status of Civil Servants NC0805115894 Cairo MENA in Arabic 1135 GMT 8 May 94 NC0805115894 Cairo MENA Arabic BFN [Text] Tunis, 8 May (MENA)--PLO Chairman Yasir 'Arafat has issued a decree considering all Palestinian employees in various administrations in the occupied territories as employees of the Palestinian National Authority. Jibril al-Rujub, 'Arafat's adviser for the occupied territories affairs, said 'Arafat had decided to appoint Lawyer Ghassan al-Shak'ah as provisional mayor of Nabulus until elections are held in the self-rule areas in the future.
